overview_description.description: Inova Energia Solar specializes in the provision of photovoltaic energy solutions. The company offers services such as the installation of residential and commercial solar power plants. They provide solar panels with a power output of 400W to 450W, capable of generating up to 3,000 kWh per month. Inova Energia Solar also offers project development services, helping customers to generate their own electricity. The company's offerings are aimed at enabling customers to harness solar energy, reducing their reliance on traditional electricity sources and promoting sustainable energy use.
